# Copy to .env.local and adjust as needed.

# Base URL of the FastAPI backend. Leave unset to use a same-origin request:
# in dev, Vite proxies /faces, /products, /health to http://localhost:8000
# (see vite.config.ts); in production the frontend build is served by the
# same FastAPI app. Only set this if the backend runs on a different host.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000
